reviews.review_text: Dont tell me this town Some great energy this night particularly with Shakedown, Hes gone and Black Peter. Brent streams seemlessly into and out of some of the older tunes. Nice punch opening with Alabama and a cruising first set. Second set is fuller, cheers to another wonderful show.
